{"tid":1242051,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺大家都好似誤會咗啲嘢","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T02:48:37.000Z","uid":38780,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"df29f046ae4038be72437477b008d276ecc1aeb7","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"監警會琴日係記者會都講得好清楚<br />\n任何人都可以就住某一件事件作出投訴 <br />\n唔一定係當事人先可以投訴<br />\n<br />\n可以有人話<br />\n監狗會咪即係自己人查自己人 有鳩用咩<br />\n<br />\n但係唔投訴先係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無用</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家要一齊去投訴 證明佢有幾咁廢<br />\n咁到時佢迫到上身 一定要做嘢 如果唔做嘢即係廢<br />\n咁樣先證實到啲嘢出黎<br />\n而唔係 屌都無鳩用架啦 搞咁撚多做乜<br />\n<br />\n如果大家唔投訴班黑警<br />\n班黑警就只會覺得自己打完人唔使負責<br />\n就自去到最尾真係乜嘢都無做到<br />\n都最少證明到畀全香港人睇監警會有幾廢<br />\n可以促請政府再跟進！！<br />\n唔好畀政府有借口<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我地一直都有個有效既方法去投訴 or 你投訴咗再講啦<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要做啲嘢 唔係喺到放負 係到講無鳩用架啦<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb306fb198ce6f175e0eab86f7d825e3bacebf3","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c7effdc56c964d96efb646d22389f0a0c1aac7b","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:27:44.000Z","msg":"大家要投佢老母 <br />\n投到佢畀回應我地<br />\n投佢唔做嘢都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2569b057c2cccca2c5e1701302295da36ba2ebeb","tid":1242051,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a3a4161eab3107e7dbfe8448714c11c0fabfe76","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:29:13.000Z","msg":"大家有時間去屌鳩黑警同時都可以去監狗會投訴！<br />\n唔好畀佢用數字講大話"},{"pid":"4dca7e5a209d9cabc0ca6122fc08d03e8cacf279","tid":1242051,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"梁定邦啱啱上任監警主席一週年 希望佢做到野"},{"pid":"11faa51fe0e3948e086cc215304bfdf421401699","tid":1242051,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abadf9685d0bd018cd42051eb65e88bb5f241b80","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dca7e5a209d9cabc0ca6122fc08d03e8cacf279","tid":1242051,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"梁定邦啱啱上任監警主席一週年 希望佢做到野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"佢做唔做嘢都好<br />\n贏既一定我地<br />\n佢唔做嘢即刻表示監警會無作用<br />\n佢做嘢就可以寧個班亂鳩咁打既黑警負責！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a14fb800cd8f2e8da7b10eefdaf7849854a82f","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65e96e6b98a35afc05dc98a876cfe7b9c418f91d","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:32:59.000Z","msg":"大家千奇唔好怕上身<br />\n如果你為正確既事情發聲都係錯既話<br />\n咁仲有咩係正確！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575d9f1dd88094ed5740592c44a55d8db808f203","tid":1242051,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:33:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1d4e1224d3be052de39d74cb5ef3f5baa1c139a","tid":1242051,"uid":111006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"一定要投，乜野方法都好，全撚部要投"},{"pid":"14bcc7651b92fc0cc616e8a9e6a59ec7b2194b38","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:36:54.000Z","msg":"之前都有隊友講過<br />\n<br />\n舉個例子咁<br />\n好民陣喺中信門口搞和平集會，不反對通知書都出埋，完全合法。如果參加一個咁樣既集會都要驚既，其實你已經失去左免於恐懼既自由。"},{"pid":"e9786ba51b206d8da5f9b43f8c2818e9b5baf4ec","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:38:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我地要投訴班狗<br />\n等佢地唔好以為乜撚都唔洗負責<br />\n打人係要有代價架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92c1a978dc8da354451a64dc47b944bd9d2831c","tid":1242051,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}